{"tid":2305430,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"《未圓》（原：My Bonnie Lies over the Ocean）","createTime":"2020-11-29T15:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T00:40:10.000Z","uid":66909,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f5c9713fb395da2b781dc9264530f6fa45f3c842","tid":2305430,"uid":66909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:29:07.000Z","msg":"《未圓》<br />\n改編自《My Bonnie Lies over the Ocean》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n榮光顯照漆黑天與地<br />\n昂首因信仰是與非<br />\n從不知愛幾多分熾熱<br />\n能落得教別人念記<br />\n<br />\nBring back　Bring back<br />\n掃著日曆沒完沒了變少<br />\nBring back　Bring back<br />\n訴著舊夢未圓未了<br />\n<br />\n留低這副身軀倘有用<br />\n離開之旅有浪有風<br />\n浮生不見漂於千里外<br />\n沉沒音訊尚餘是痛<br />\n<br />\nBring back　Bring back<br />\n掃著日曆沒完沒了變少<br />\nBring back　Bring back<br />\n訴著舊夢未圓未了<br />\n<br />\n皇天請看這彎曲世道<br />\n人間掙扎尺地寸土<br />\n如果需要找一生確幸<br />\n難道失散便尋獲到<br />\n<br />\nBring back　Bring back<br />\n掃著日曆沒完沒了變少<br />\nBring back　Bring back<br />\n訴著舊夢未圓未了<br />\n<br />\n榮光顯照漆黑中禁地<br />\n籠中羈鳥盼望遠飛<br />\n還不知愛幾多分價値<br />\n才値得百萬人念記<br />\n<br />\nBring back　Bring back<br />\n掃著日曆沒完沒了變少<br />\nBring back　Bring back<br />\n訴著舊夢未圓未了"},{"pid":"cceedb1d0b44e397b2116061153959c883bca4e9","tid":2305430,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c58dc9b4a8cf505052eb1c27fbcdb6545dd28c","tid":2305430,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:44:18.000Z","msg":"好勤力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ab4c2ff87bfbbc1821b13735b524cc4a68e2f3","tid":2305430,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T16:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9ac7d53a1699141adfff0b2727cc23b2d848fa","tid":2305430,"uid":302951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T18:56:09.000Z","msg"